{"tid":1013798,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉欣祝賭王長命千歲 繼續提供娛樂給大家","createTime":"2019-02-08T15:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T03:03:13.000Z","uid":51469,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"96d3629d594dfa329d9b7e95514220b3c52baf00","tid":1013798,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T15:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images2.sina.com/newscenter/sinacn/502-104-103-107/2008-11-25/1227671411_LiS3wl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages2.sina.com%2Fnewscenter%2Fsinacn%2F502-104-103-107%2F2008-11-25%2F1227671411_LiS3wl.jpg&h=b2d8ae3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180714/2_603363_0/-%E7%B6%93%E5%85%B8-%E5%AF%8C%E8%B1%AA%E5%A9%86%E5%AA%B3%E5%82%B3%E4%B8%8D%E5%92%8C-%E5%98%89%E6%AC%A3%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E5%90%8C%E6%9E%B1%E9%A3%9F%E9%A3%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A1-BB%E4%BE%86%E4%BA%86%E5%B8%B6%E5%9F%8B%E8%80%81%E7%88%BA%E5%A5%B6%E5%A5%B6%E5%8E%BB%E7%8E%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180714%2F2_603363_0%2F-%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%2585%25B8-%25E5%25AF%258C%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E5%25A9%2586%25E5%25AA%25B3%25E5%2582%25B3%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2592%258C-%25E5%2598%2589%25E6%25AC%25A3%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%259E%25B1%25E9%25A3%259F%25E9%25A3%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25AD%25A1-BB%25E4%25BE%2586%25E4%25BA%2586%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E5%259F%258B%25E8%2580%2581%25E7%2588%25BA%25E5%25A5%25B6%25E5%25A5%25B6%25E5%258E%25BB%25E7%258E%25A9&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1MQ0GhOv7yEvjYTsEPvBCF8%3D&h=384cff8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180714%2F2_603363_0%2F-%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%2585%25B8-%25E5%25AF%258C%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E5%25A9%2586%25E5%25AA%25B3%25E5%2582%25B3%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2592%258C-%25E5%2598%2589%25E6%25AC%25A3%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%259E%25B1%25E9%25A3%259F%25E9%25A3%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25AD%25A1-BB%25E4%25BE%2586%25E4%25BA%2586%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E5%259F%258B%25E8%2580%2581%25E7%2588%25BA%25E5%25A5%25B6%25E5%25A5%25B6%25E5%258E%25BB%25E7%258E%25A9&h=4eb705a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180714/2_603363_0/-%E7%B6%93%E5%85%B8-%E5%AF%8C%E8%B1%AA%E5%A9%86%E5%AA%B3%E5%82%B3%E4%B8%8D%E5%92%8C-%E5%98%89%E6%AC%A3%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E5%90%8C%E6%9E%B1%E9%A3%9F%E9%A3%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A1-BB%E4%BE%86%E4%BA%86%E5%B8%B6%E5%9F%8B%E8%80%81%E7%88%BA%E5%A5%B6%E5%A5%B6%E5%8E%BB%E7%8E%A9</a><br />\n<br />\n許晉亨和李嘉欣在拍拖兩年，修成正果，於零八年結婚，他們結婚當日，又撞啱許晉亨前外父賭王何鴻燊在珍寶海鮮舫擺農曆生日壽宴，傳媒於是問他想不想許晉亨以後不要再婚？賭王就話：「可能佢（許晉亨）再結多十趟八趟都唔定。」正所謂港姐是美貌與智慧並重， 瑪利諾中學畢業的李嘉欣，是八八年港姐冠軍，你又知唔知佢點答賭王？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n面對賭王「贈興」，李嘉欣反而話：「<strong>最緊要佢（賭王）老人家生日快樂，祝佢長命千歲，繼續提供娛樂話題俾大家，等大家有得寫有得問。</strong>」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘉欣隨咗巧妙地回應賭王，她都有其他金句。好似結婚當日，當攝影師夏永康要求嘉欣擺多點甫士時，嘉欣就話：「今日我淨係要攬實我老公。」嘩，仲唔冧爆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n零四年，傳出李嘉欣夥拍內地影帝胡軍演出關錦鵬執導的內地劇《畫魂》，期間傳出被內地富豪照顧，嘉欣大口氣話：「我就是富商，不需被包養。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n面對外間經常笑指她和老爺奶奶關係麻麻，與及同枱食飯不歡而散，嘉欣面對種種指責，她話：「如果食飯真係食完會黑面，就唔會一齊食啦！大家時間好寶貴，如果唔開心，點會一齊食飯！」而嘉欣嫁作許家媳婦後，就做導遊帶埋老爺奶奶去玩，一一年她更誕下男嬰Jayden Max。"},{"pid":"7ea651d595cb054a3840e5d55ce7f07bb20d2665","tid":1013798,"uid":23832,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T15:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WaVa4PH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWaVa4PH.png&h=12aed238&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n預咗個post又會好嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f0d786e58c8d688e9a4cdb6a7e50b49d677e96","tid":1013798,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T15:48:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79819c9aeb06d12c57b00990fb14b9500fa5e069","tid":101379